{"tid":1495020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【記者請入】林鄭、散仔成日話監警會有用，但無人提過呢樣嘢","createTime":"2019-08-22T01:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T01:38:52.000Z","uid":64981,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6414dae1bab5cee76627bb43bce4fa63dc2cd3","tid":1495020,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"監警會今年踏入成立十周年，《蘋果》整理過往9年的統計數字，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現在現行機制下，每年只得3%至4%投訴最終成立</span>，約九成的受罰警員只是被警告或訓諭。數字亦揭露警方視監警會的質詢如「耳邊風」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2017/18年度涉及行使警權的質詢，警方的接受率為0%；至於將投訴結果由不屬實改為屬實的個案，只佔總個案約1%。</span></span>有民間團體批評監警會是「無牙老虎」，建議授權該會調查嚴重個案，以保障公眾利益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190605/59672079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190605%2F59672079&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=58a77209\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190605%2F59672079&h=a5ff3fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190605/59672079</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">監警會質詢散仔，但散仔接受率係0%，咁我要監警會黎托呀？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c90ab20e55d6f8aaa9dc50a6324fd120242aeea3","tid":1495020,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ed397af515712d688e175897bfffe46879ba22","tid":1495020,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"借post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">前線以後噴漆<br />\n請噴英文！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" 